Storytlr is an open source lifestreaming and micro blogging platform. You can use it for a single user
or it can act as a host for many people all from the same installation.

Released under an Apache 2.0 License (see LICENSE).
All documentation and tutorials available on http://storytlr.org

This is the ongoing development branch. We are doing our best to keep things stable. 
Shout if you think it has been broken !
